Package it.polimi.ingsw.controller

Enum GamePhase

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<GamePhase>
it.polimi.ingsw.controller.GamePhase
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<GamePhase>, java.lang.constant.Constable
public enum GamePhase
extends java.lang.Enum<GamePhase>
GamePhase is the enumeration for all match's phases. The main game-phases are: initial-info, when players decide a nickname and colour; choose-gods, when the god-chooser selects some gods and every player chooses the one he/she wants to play with; game-preparation, when every player places the workers on the board; real-game, when the real match is played; match-ended, the phase that follows a match; match-lost, phase for who lost a match.
